Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.27,0:01:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浪客剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.11,0:01:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你胡说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.15,0:01:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,般若他们怎么可能死了 你骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.15,0:01:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.15,0:01:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,般若他们四个人为了保护苍紫\N已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.79,0:02:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,般若他们不可能那么容易死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.83,0:02:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道般若他们很厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.36,0:02:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.47,0:02:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刀剑终究敌不过枪炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.70,0:02:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们真的已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.61,0:02:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫就是为了替他们四人报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才要杀害剑心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.88,0:02:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为杀死剑心就能证明\N御庭帮在江湖中的地位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.45,0:02:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.63,0:02:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四十二话\N苍紫与志志雄结盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.11,0:02:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.81,0:02:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是头一个来我们这儿的外人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别误会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.88,0:03:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来打听绯村剑心的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.22,0:03:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没兴趣和你们打交道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.73,0:03:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种高傲的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.73,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是无法成为我的部下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我倒蛮欣赏你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.37,0:03:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲着这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.57,0:03:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是会提供你\N绯村剑心的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.08,0:03:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是要我帮你\N打倒绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.09,0:03:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以为了自己与绯村决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.62,0:03:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要帮我解决他也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.59,0:03:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的知道绯村的下落吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.50,0:03:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只知道他和张十刀的决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这我也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.60,0:03:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个叫老翁是御庭帮的成员\N曾帮助过绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.51,0:04:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这老头一定知道\N绯村剑心的落脚处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以去突击\N老翁的住处葵屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.92,0:04:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逼问他  或许可以问一些情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.56,0:04:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  御庭帮的老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.57,0:04:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操  你的苍紫离开葵屋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.24,0:04:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操一早起来看不到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定又要大哭一场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.72,0:04:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操的事我已拜托老翁了\N别担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.82,0:04:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这真的没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还真嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.63,0:04:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御庭帮现在就靠我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.77,0:05:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们与老大同进退共生死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.41,0:05:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都听老大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.18,0:05:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能打败绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.08,0:05:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是江湖中最强的帮派了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.02,0:05:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样要不要去抓老翁来问问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.99,0:05:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.06,0:05:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能杀了绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.63,0:05:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后我们就是一家人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.47,0:05:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子好吗\N那个苍紫虽然武功不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.34,0:05:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看他能出卖朋友\N也是个心狠手辣的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.38,0:05:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不也全都是\N心狠手辣的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.92,0:05:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓物竞天择  弱肉强食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.46,0:06:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.86,0:06:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刀子挥动过头\N力道就会使不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.86,0:06:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看清楚再出刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.17,0:06:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你的腕力如此迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.81,0:06:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了  这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.65,0:06:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄的势力更猖狂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快教我飞天御剑的精髓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.39,0:07:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这招式是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.99,0:07:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞天御剑流二段拔刀术“双龙闪”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.43,0:07:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这种招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.84,0:07:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完了  以刀鞘击剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.97,0:07:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是二段拔刀术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.11,0:07:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“双龙闪雷”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.32,0:07:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这种功力\N也想跟我学飞天御剑流吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个笨徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.56,0:07:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先通过我这关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再教你飞天御剑的精髓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.30,0:07:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  快上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.10,0:07:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在发什么呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.78,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心的眼光一点也不迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.15,0:08:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前教你飞天御剑流时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.57,0:08:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别以为我在刁难你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.71,0:08:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这是在训练你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.71,0:08:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别发呆了  快出招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.88,0:08:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再不出招就学不到功夫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.53,0:08:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是枭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.16,0:08:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枭是专门在夜晚偷袭的部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.80,0:08:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御庭帮的巢穴就像鼠辈的窝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.50,0:08:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀老鼠对枭而言\N是轻而易举的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.96,0:09:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.43,0:09:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.46,0:09:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.21,0:09:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.21,0:09:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的伙伴都被抓了\N你再叫也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.35,0:09:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是志志雄派来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是来问剑心下落的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.95,0:09:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.20,0:10:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么去那么久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.97,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.14,0:10:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道夜枭部队全被打败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.51,0:10:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好一支神勇的夜枭部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.22,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老翁是唯一能与前任\N御庭帮帮主相提并论的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.97,0:10:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正午时刻在阿田处等你\N一个人来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.27,0:10:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是御庭帮的暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.84,0:10:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老翁要找你单挑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.82,0:10:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你非得\N把御庭帮的面子丢尽的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就先把我给杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.00,0:11:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一天终于要来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.19,0:11:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老翁出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.47,0:11:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.77,0:11:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我  老翁究竟去哪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.61,0:11:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到爷爷穿着武士服\N还拿着武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.95,0:11:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老翁和苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.35,0:11:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.63,0:12:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.80,0:12:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你休想做出对御庭帮不利的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.01,0:12:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则你就先把我杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.51,0:12:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想这么做 但是你逼我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在阿田处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.23,0:12:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在去也来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.30,0:12:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不能不让他去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.67,0:12:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个是亲人  一个是爱人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.88,0:12:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去哪一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.81,0:12:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是令人痛苦的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.26,0:13:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷  苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.53,0:13:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葵屋突击失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.44,0:13:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫已亲自出马了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.08,0:13:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫已经去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.11,0:13:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.12,0:13:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信有地狱存在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.32,0:13:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.66,0:13:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不相信无论好人坏人\N死后都回归尘土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.83,0:13:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许你不信  但我相信地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.20,0:13:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说有个杀不死的绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.57,0:14:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四乃森苍紫为了除掉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.81,0:14:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以背叛自己的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.95,0:14:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更可以将那个叫老翁的\N老好人杀成重伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.35,0:14:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就像想用火烧死\N我的日本政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经过这次血的教训
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.53,0:14:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终于认清 人世间其实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.63,0:14:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是个名符其实的地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.20,0:14:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你还是想不透的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.74,0:14:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让你见识一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.13,0:14:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是钢刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.40,0:14:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从前代帮主那儿得知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.63,0:14:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钢刀是刀剑的克星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.80,0:15:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的小太刀二刀流打不倒我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水流招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.65,0:15:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的得意招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.25,0:15:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉着变幻莫测的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.09,0:15:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分散对手的注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.37,0:15:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的\N小太刀二刀流阴阳交叉法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.34,0:15:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前代帮主的小太刀二刀流\N已落伍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.15,0:15:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论钢铁\N无论是你还是绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.75,0:15:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都逃不过我的\N小太刀二刀流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手  老翁、苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.94,0:16:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼前这个苍紫武功高强\N已不是我所认识的苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.54,0:16:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷酷与无情\N已将其潜力完全发挥出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快告诉我绯村剑心的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.49,0:16:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就放你一条生路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.83,0:16:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会和你一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.53,0:16:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出卖自己的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.28,0:16:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我就先杀了你\N再去解决葵屋内的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.15,0:16:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你休想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会拼了我的老命\N与你决斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.49,0:17:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让绯村快去解决\N志志雄那个恶魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心了  苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.55,0:17:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的轰钓棍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.56,0:17:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.86,0:17:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.89,0:17:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是回天剑舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.16,0:17:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六连
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.74,0:17:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.28,0:18:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.28,0:18:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次放过你\N下次你别在我面前出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.66,0:18:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去告诉绯村剑心\N我在志志雄那儿等他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.93,0:18:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的体温
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.94,0:18:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年前被火灼伤后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.31,0:19:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身的汗腺全被烧坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.68,0:19:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后我的体温\N就像地狱之火一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.95,0:19:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,散发着高热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.82,0:19:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种炽热将我烧醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.92,0:19:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我知道人性本恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.63,0:19:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人世其实就是个地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.60,0:19:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.44,0:19:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫平等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.74,0:19:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是骗人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.81,0:19:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有邪恶王国\N才是我志志雄建造的地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.65,0:19:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  方治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.42,0:19:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很可怕吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.45,0:19:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我太感动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.46,0:19:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有依赖你这位伟人\N我们才能建立新的日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.10,0:19:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄  我真是太高兴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.57,0:20:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又一个忠实的支持者产生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.84,0:20:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身缝合共计一百三十八针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.28,0:20:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生说如果能活是奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.72,0:20:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是随时都会死的意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.98,0:20:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.22,0:20:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫已经失去人性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哭吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.40,0:20:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还是不够坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.96,0:20:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操不过是个十六岁的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.44,0:20:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个年纪本来就是多愁善感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.91,0:20:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是老翁留下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.22,0:20:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说如果他发生不测\N就把它交给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.16,0:21:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我最亲爱的孙子阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.87,0:21:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.94,0:21:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你读到这封信时\N我已经不在人世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.64,0:21:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必太悲伤\N因为我已完成我应尽的义务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.02,0:21:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御庭帮到今天已正式解散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.89,0:21:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后的事情就交给绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.62,0:21:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.06,0:21:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该恢复平民的身分\N过普通的生活就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.13,0:21:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.07,0:21:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.01,0:21:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 以后我将代替四乃林苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.02,0:21:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做你们的帮主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.99,0:22:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.82,0:22:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要和绯村共同努力\N打败志志雄这群恶魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.76,0:22:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论敌人是谁\N即使是四乃森苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.10,0:22:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也格杀勿论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.63,0:22:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.04,0:22:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捍卫御庭帮的\N保护各位的生命安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.21,0:22:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御庭帮的各位就是我的家人\N我和我的家人共生死共存亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.79,0:22:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  你绝对不能这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.76,0:22:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操   这不是儿戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.39,0:22:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是阿操  以后叫我帮主
